title: Live: NSW Now: Sculpture by the Sea to stay in Bondi, NSW boosts COVID-19 mental health support
description: MORNING BRIEFING: A Bondi outdoor sculpture exhibition will make its return on October 22 if public gathering restrictions are lifted, while the NSW Government announces plans to bolster the mental healthcare workforce.
